name: "Banana Farts" by Sunny Crittenden (digital, 2019)
description: This is the 2nd digital drawing I ever did. It was created on a Samsung Galaxy tablet with the Adobe Draw app & an analog stylus on August 9th, 2019. This is a portrait of a modern marriage. I'm minting this on Hic Et Nunc on April 22nd, 2021 in honour of Earth Day, in an edition of 60. Any remaining editions on April 1st, 2022 will be burned. For the full story, go here: http://sunnycrittenden.com/wp/2021/04/23/my-1st-drop-with-hic-et-nunc/
